---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="What I Do" description="Danièle Lydon works with actors in film, theatre and television, and with business clients on voice, accent and communication.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">The work</p>
      <h1>What I Do</h1>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">I love my work. The journey taken with actors and individuals to achieve something — endlessly rewarding.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" id="actors">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <div class="content-block__label">
          <p class="eyebrow">For Actors</p>
          <div class="gold-rule"></div>
          <h2>Accent &amp; Dialect</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content-block__body">
          <p>I have often found there are two things that can hijack an actor's confidence: Dialect and Costume. If they are not right, it can really impede the actor's embodiment of the character, not to mention their enjoyment. I have no say in the costume — although I can help with finding breath support when corseted tightly in a period drama!</p>
          <p>I work to help find a route into any given accent or dialect which works for the individual. Initially working from your own accent starting point, then finding a route specific to you to achieve the required dialect needed to bring your character to life authentically.</p>
          <p>I also work with the text: developing the voice, support, resonance, range and articulation — and having the skills to fill any given space safely.</p>
          <p>I work with individuals and groups.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <section class="section" id="business">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <div class="content-block__label">
          <p class="eyebrow">For Business</p>
          <div class="gold-rule"></div>
          <h2>Voice &amp; Communication</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content-block__body">
          <p>Within the business world I work with those who would like to soften their accent, those who experience vocal fatigue at the end of a meeting or day, and those who want to develop a greater impact in how they communicate.</p>
          <p>I help to strengthen presentation skills and develop confident, relaxed communication — whether in individual meetings or group situations, informal or formal. The confidence to speak and be heard.</p>
          <p>I look at how to use your voice and body language for maximum impact. To develop and understand the tools of great speaking. To let that message land.</p>
          <p>I work in a safe, fun and supportive way to help you practically acquire the tools to communicate authentically with impact and purpose. It's important to stay authentic.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section section--grey">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Business clients include</p>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <div class="client-list">
        <span>NHS Imperial Healthcare Trust</span>
        <span>The Welsh Government</span>
        <span>WIG (Whitehall and Industry Group)</span>
        <span>Hiscox Insurance Group</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get started</p>
